er","description":"Formal identifier for this agent","ref":"0","effectiveId":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/identifier"},{"path":["_anyOf","3","cdi:image"],"id":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/image","description":"Image associated with this agent","ref":"1","effectiveId":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/image"},{"path":["_anyOf","0","cdi:individualName","cdi:sex"],"id":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/sex","description":"Sex specification associated with this name","effectiveId":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/sex"},{"path":["_anyOf","0","cdi:individualName","cdi:sex","cdi:sexCode"],"id":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/sexCode","description":"Code identifying sex (e.g. ISO 5218 values)","schema_type":"string","effectiveId":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/sexCode"},{"path":["_anyOf","0","cdi:individualName","cdi:typeOfIndividualName"],"id":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/typeOfIndividualName","description":"Classification of this name (e.g. birth, married, pen)","effectiveId":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/typeOfIndividualName"},{"path":["_anyOf","0","cdi:individualName","cdi:context"],"id":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/context","description":"Context or usage of this name","effectiveId":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/context"},{"path":["_anyOf","0","cdi:individualName","cdi:context","cdi:vocabulary"],"id":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/vocabulary","description":"A reference to the external controlled vocabulary, using a URI or other resolvable identifier.","effectiveId":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/vocabulary"},{"path":["_anyOf","0","cdi:individualName","cdi:context","cdi:valueForOther"],"id":"http://ddialliance.org/Specification/DDI-CDI/1.0/RDF/valueForOther","description":"If